author: The Associated Press
title: The top 10 audiobooks on Audible.com
text:
Audible.com best-sellers for week ending Oct. 9, 2015:
Fiction
1. Locke & Key by Joe Hill and Gabriel Rodriguez, narrated by Haley Joel Osment, Tatiana Maslany, Kate Mulgrew and a full cast (Audible Studios)
2. The Martian by Andy Weir, narrated by R.C. Bray (Podium Publishing)
3. The Survivor by Vince Flynn and Kyle Mills, narrated by George Guidall (Simon & Schuster Audio)
4. Shadows of Self by Brandon Sanderson, narrated by Michael Kramer (Macmillan Audio)
5. A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms by George R. R. Martin, narrated by Harry Lloyd (Random House Audio)
6. The Girl in the Spider's Web: A Lisbeth Salander Novel by David Lagercrantz, narrated by Simon Vance (Random House Audio)
7. The Sword of Summer by Rick Riordan, narrated by Christopher Guetig (Listening Library)
8. The Aeronaut's Windlass by Jim Butcher, narrated by Euan Morton (Penguin Audio)
9. Angelmaker by Nick Harkaway, narrated by Daniel Weyman (Blackstone Audio, Inc.)
10. Orphan's Inheritance by Aline Ohanesian, narrated by Assaf Cohen (HighBridge Company)
Nonfiction
1. Simple Rules: How to Thrive in a Complex World by Donald Sull and Kathleen M. Eisenhardt, narrated by Jeff Cummings (Brilliance Audio)
2. Why Not Me? By Mindy Kaling, narrated by Mindy Kaling, Greg Daniels and B.J. Novak (Random House Audio)
3. Rising Strong by Brene Brown, narrated by the author (Random House Audio)
4. Killing Reagan by Bill O'Reilly and Martin Dugard, narrated by Bill O'Reilly (Macmillan Audio)
5. Big Magic: Creative Living Beyond Fear by Elizabeth Gilbert, narrated by the author (Penguin Audio)
6. Furiously Happy: A Funny Book About Horrible Things by Jenny Lawson, narrated by the author (Macmillan Audio)
7. So You Want to Start a Brewery? The Lagunitas Story by Tony Magee, narrated by Brett Barry (Audible Studios)
8. The Power of I Am: Two Words That Will Change Your Life Today by Joel Osteen, narrated by the author (Hachette Audio)
9. The Life-Changing Magic of Tidying Up: The Japanese Art of Decluttering and Organizing by Marie Kondo, narrated by Emily Woo Zeller (Tantor Audio)
10. Elon Musk: Tesla, SpaceX, and the Quest for a Fantastic Future by Ashlee Vance, narrated by Fred Sanders (Harper Audio)
___
